    "body": "@dream960727 have you considered using an SSH tunnel to your remote node? For example:\r\n\r\n```\r\nssh -L 8545:127.0.0.1:8545 user@example.com\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis would forward your local port 8545 to the local 8545 port on the remote node, without exposing it externally.",
